sequenceDiagram
    actor Dev as Dev team
    actor Alice
    actor Bob
    participant Chain as IOTA mainnet
    participant Scanner as Our scanner

    Dev->>Chain: Deploy tx — publish marketplace package
    Note over Chain: Package + modules now live on-chain

    Alice->>Chain: Tx — list NFT 42 for 100 IOTA
    Note right of Chain: creates 1 Listing object<br/>emits 1 ListEvent

    Bob->>Chain: Tx — buy NFT 42
    Note right of Chain: transfers NFT to Bob<br/>destroys Listing object<br/>emits SaleEvent + FeeEvent<br/>(1 tx → 3 object changes, 2 events)

    Note over Scanner: every 6 hours
    Scanner->>Chain: "any new events from tracked projects?"
    Chain-->>Scanner: [ListEvent, SaleEvent, FeeEvent, ...]
    Scanner->>Scanner: count per project, save snapshot
